:::


Alternatively, we can plot precision-recall curves.


::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
autoplot(bmr, type = "prc")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-39-1.png){fig-align='center' width=672}
